Package: CopyNumberPlots
Type: Package
Title: Create Copy-Number Plots using karyoploteR's functionality.
Version: 0.1.12
Author: Bernat Gel (bgel@igtp.cat) and Miriam Magallon <mmagallon@igtp.cat>
Maintainer: Bernat Gel <bgel@igtp.cat>
Description: CopyNumberPlots have a set of functions extending karyoploteR's 
functionality to create beatiful, customizable and flexible plots of 
copy-number related data.
